# 2024 CS Warsaw Cup

Vladimir Samoilov
| championwomen = Katherine Medland Spence
| championpairs =  Anastasiia Metelkinaand Luka Berulava
| championdance =  Evgeniia Loparevaand Geoffrey Brissaud
| previouscomp = 2023 CS Warsaw Cup
| nextcomp = 2025 CS Warsaw Cup
| previouscs = 2024 CS Tallinn Trophy
| nextcs = 2024 CS Golden Spin of Zagreb
}}
The 2024 CS Warsaw Cup was held on November 20–24, 2024, in Warsaw, Poland. It was part of the 2024–25 ISU Challenger Series. Medals were awarded in men's singles, women's singles, pairs, and ice dance.
Entries
The International Skating Union published the list of entries on October 29, 2024.
